<div id="review_32050839" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/32050839" />
    <a title="Karen" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/778546-karen"><img alt="Karen" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1231050177p2/778546.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/32050839?book_show_action=true">Sep 04, 2008</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Karen" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Karen" href="/user/show/778546-karen">Karen</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="really liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">really liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer32050839" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer1649594157611997321">Overall I enjoyed this book. Colorful description of Kit Carson and the American West. I can only imagine how the Native Americans, especially the Navajo, would describe Carson and his ilk, though.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


      <div class="reviewFooter uitext buttons">
          

