        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2812652522" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer10143059048355064959">A thoroughly researched and elegantly recorded history of the American frontier west in conjunction with biographical portrait of Kit Carson and those around him both friend and foe. </span>

          </span>
        </div>


